nodes.text: Mission to the Imperial supply depot

During the Galactic Civil War, a group of Rebel Alliance agents undertook a mission to an Imperial supply depot in the Rainos Cluster. The objective of the mission was to retrieve from the supply depot replacement KL-45 coolant hydro-valves that were needed to prevent the destruction of an Alliance base on the nearby planet Obas.
